      "date": "2022-07-29 00:47:22.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIt isn't really clear to me why it is useful to add a configure check that is checking for a #define that can be checked directly in the code?\n\nIf you prefer to have the #ifdef checks using HAVE_ZFS_PROJECT_QUOTA, then it would be possible to add a single check in osd_internal.h:\n\n #ifdef ZFS_PROJINHERIT          /* since ZFS 0.8.0 */\n #define HAVE_ZFS_PROJECT_QUOTA\n #endif\n\nor similar?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
